{"tid":1984212,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"尚‧珒溋加推 醫護人員額外享1%折扣","createTime":"2020-04-22T10:06:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T05:59:35.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e8eea521c01fc7d540dc0444db84871095915c0d","tid":1984212,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T10:06:15.000Z","msg":"龍湖集團及合景泰富集團合作發展的啟德尚‧珒溋，剛加推新一批單位，新增醫護人員置業折扣優惠。合景泰富集團市務及營銷總監 (香港及海外) 張詩韻表示，面積由332至1072方呎，提供1至4房戶，部分單位更獲優先認購車位優惠。<br />\n<br />\n龍湖集團香港營銷總監黃少鴻表示，為答謝香港醫護人員盡心守護巿民的健康，現特設「醫護人員置業折扣」，為售價1%，最高19%折扣優惠；扣除最高19%折扣後，售價由1274萬至2310.64萬，呎價23462至30727元，折後平均呎價26756元 ；以一般買家享18%折扣計算，折實平均價約27087元。<br />\n<br />\n項目亦公布銷售安排，於本周五合共發售138伙，其中以先到先得形式銷售72伙，另以招標方式發售66伙。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200420/_2020042021205486990.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200420%2F_2020042021205486990.jpeg&h=460a2451&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79a88100e5d3da41a0eeb8c9249d65ec09f91cd1","tid":1984212,"uid":36563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T10:07:20.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8b321b4a39cecfccdd1595c343550de70543ff","tid":1984212,"uid":49336,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T10:07:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真好 醫護不能死 你還要供樓"},{"pid":"57bc7342ef1837b19d3d7ac8b7010b2a017b18fa","tid":1984212,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T10:07:50.000Z","msg":"俾完首期就爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361d4ff5b9a33775caf444150a49974d7624f05f","tid":1984212,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T10:18:08.000Z","msg":"條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c6ae4a9a4f3b98cf60525102b08eb